HEADWORD: Nidget
<hw>Nidg"et</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>nigget</asp>, <asp>nigeot</asp>.]</altsp> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>nigaud</ets> a booby, fool, OF. <ets>niger</ets> to play the
fool.]</ety> <def>A fool; an idiot, a coward.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Camden.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
